data.title: Yuvika Chaudhary Evicted From 'Bigg Boss Nau'
data.meta_description: She is the fifth contestant from the show to get eliminated. Her partner Vikas and Gujarati singer Arvind Vegda got evicted on November 1.

Bollywood actor Richa Chadha has always being known for her intense character but while she has no qualms on doing a candy floss role as well but she does not aspire to become a complete candy floss actress and wishes she work with Shah Rukh Khan.
